<p>Tomb Raider: Definitive Edition is available via the Nintendo eShop for £17/$20. That said, owners of Aspyr's previously released Tomb Raider 1-3 Remastered Starring Lara Croft or Tomb Raider 4-6 Remastered on Nintendo Switch are eligible for a 10 percent discount. </p>
<figure>
 


<figcaption><span>Image credit: <cite>Crystal Dynamics</cite></span></figcaption>
</figure>
<p>For more on the series, <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/rhianna-pratchetts-stories-from-the-tomb-raider-reboot">a few years ago I spoke with Tomb Raider 2013 writer Rhianna Pratchett about her time on the game</a>.</p>
<p>More recently, <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/heres-our-first-trailer-for-netflixs-tomb-raider-the-legend-of-lara-croft-season-two">Netflix shared a trailer for the second season of its Tomb Raider anime</a>, known as The Legend of Lara Croft.</p>

